'''弗罗因德尔·杰罗姆·斯图亚特'''（'''Freundel Jerome Stuart'''，{{bd|1951年|4月27日|catIdx=S}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.caribbeanconference.org/speakers.php |title=Caribbean MBA Conference |publisher=Caribbeanconference.org |date= |accessdate=2013-02-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104071038/http://www.caribbeanconference.org/speakers.php |archivedate=2013-01-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gisbarbados.gov.bb/index.php?categoryid=43 |title=BGIS Media - Biography - Deputy Prime Minister |publisher=Gisbarbados.gov.bb |date= |accessdate=2013-02-23 |archive-date=2010-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326224706/http://www.gisbarbados.gov.bb/index.php?categoryid=43 |dead-url=no }}</ref>是[[巴巴多斯总理|第7任巴巴多斯总理]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Breaking News: Cabinet members to be re-confirmed this afternoon |author=Staff writers |first= |last= |authorlink= |authorlink2= |url=http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=13545 |agency= |newspaper=[[The_Barbados_Advocate|The Barbados Advocate]] |publisher= |location= |isbn= |issn= |oclc= |pmid= |pmd= |bibcode= |doi= |id= |date=2010-10-23 |page= |pages= |at= |accessdate=2010-10-23 |trans_title= |quote= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311121239/http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=13545 |archivedate=2012-03-11|ref= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>他接替了2010年10月23日因为胰腺癌去世的[[戴維·湯普森|戴維·湯普森]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Urgent Barbados Death: Barbados Prime Minister David Thompson is dead |author=Staff writer |first= |last= |authorlink= |authorlink2= |url=http://www.cananews.net/news/131/ARTICLE/54385/2010-10-23.html |agency=[[Caribbean_News_Agency|Caribbean News Agency (CANA)]] |newspaper= |publisher= |location= |isbn= |issn= |oclc= |pmid= |pmd= |bibcode= |doi= |id= |date= |page= |pages= |at= |accessdate=2010-10-23 |trans_title= |quote= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101026145443/http://cananews.net/news/131/ARTICLE/54385/2010-10-23.html |archivedate=2010-10-26|ref= |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="PM">{{cite web|url=http://rjrnewsonline.com/news/regional/new-barbados-pm-be-sworn|title=New Barbados PM to be sworn in|date=2010-10-23|publisher=RJR News|accessdate=2010-10-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101026072507/http://rjrnewsonline.com/news/regional/new-barbados-pm-be-sworn|archivedate=2010年10月26日}}</ref>他是{{link-en|民主勞動党 (巴巴多斯)|Democratic Labour Party (Barbados)|民主勞動党}}（DLP）的成员。

==个人生活==
斯图亚特生于巴巴多斯[[圣菲利普区_(巴巴多斯)|圣菲利普区]]。<ref name=ttn>{{cite news |first= |last= |title=Barbados’ Seventh PM |url=http://www.newsday.co.tt/news/0,129706.html |work=[[Trinidad_&_Tobago's_Newsday|Trinidad & Tobago's Newsday]] |publisher= |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2010-10-25 |archive-date=2010-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028133827/http://www.newsday.co.tt/news/0,129706.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他有一个女儿，目前单身。<ref name=cwn>{{cite news|first=|last=|title=Meet Barbados' New Prime Minister|url=http://www.caribbeanworldnews.com/middle_top_news_detail.php?mid=4045|work=CaribWorldNews|publisher=|date=2010-10-23|accessdate=2010-10-25}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

他毕业于[[西印度群岛大学|西印度群岛大学]]的[[政治学|政治学]]和[[法律|法律]]专业。<ref name=cwn/>后来成为一名[[律师|律师]]。<ref name=cwn/>

==政治生涯==
弗罗因德尔·斯图亚特是{{link-en|民主勞動党 (巴巴多斯)|Democratic Labour Party (Barbados)|民主勞動党}}党员，在议会当中代表南圣迈克尔[[選區|選區]]。

==担任总理==
自2010年5月时任总理[[戴維·湯普森|戴維·湯普森]]因胰腺癌病倒后斯图亚特一直担任巴巴多斯代总理。<ref name=cwn/>2010年10月23日湯普森去世。<ref name=ttn/>民主勞動党领导人在位于[[布里奇敦|布里奇敦]]的党[[總部|總部]]召开紧急会议讨论总理的去世，在这期间，斯图亚特被选为下届总理。<ref name=ttn/> 

斯图亚特当天在[[巴巴多斯总督|总督]]监督下宣誓就职巴巴多斯第7任总理。<ref name=ttn/>

斯图亚特在2011年被任命为联合国全球可持续发展委员会的成员。

2013年2月21日斯图亚特赢得了他作为总理的第一次选举，击败了{{link-en|巴巴多斯勞動党|Barbados Labour Party}}的挑战者Noel Lynch。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=29323 |title=Winners again |work=The Barbados Advocate |accessdate=2013-02-22 |date=2013-02-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522014531/http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=29323 |archivedate=2015-05-22}}</ref>然而在五年後的選舉，他的政黨全軍覆沒，他因而下野。

